                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/phpstorm/edit/master/knpu/twig.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>The Symfony Plugin has all kinds of awesome setup for Twig integration.
So let's render a template here, <code>movie/new.html.twig</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="8526e13420">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
